Langkah Integrasi
Daftar aplikasi di Auth0 Dashboard.
Dapatkan Client ID & Secret.
Masukkan callback URL.
Ikut panduan kod di bawah (Node.js/Python/Android).
Simpan maklumat sensitif dalam .env.
Contoh Integrasi Node.js
const { auth } = require('express-openid-connect');
const config = {
  authRequired: false,
  auth0Logout: true,
  secret: process.env.AUTH0_SECRET,
  baseURL: 'https://YOUR_APP_URL',
  clientID: 'YOUR_CLIENT_ID',
  issuerBaseURL: 'https://YOUR_TENANT.auth0.com'
};
app.use(auth(config));
